Nutrients / Micronutrients

Serving Growers Since 1972




 

Beau-Ron® L
CLICK HERE TO SEE COMPLETE PRODUCT INFORMATION INCLUDING CROP USAGE, REGISTRATION AND SAFETY DATA
Beau-Ron® L is a soluble borate micronutrient designed for use as a fluid fertilizer nutrient spray additive for a variety of crop applications.
 
Features and Benefits

3.6 quarts of Beau-Ron® L provides 1 pound of elemental Boron
Soluble formulation is compatible with most liquid fertilizers
For use in foliar and soil broadcast by aerial and ground applications
Labeled for use in Field, Fruit, Nut and Vegetable crops

 
FAQ
Is Beau-Ron® L a clear liquid?
Yes, Beau-Ron® L is a clear liquid formulation containing 1.1 pound of Boron per gallon.
Will Beau-Ron® L mix with insecticides?
Beau-Ron® L will mix readily with most pesticides; however, a jar test is recommended to be positive of compatibility.
 
Always read and follow the label instructions on the product container(s) before using.







