ICYMI: Good Behavior Season 1 | TNT


Play all


        Letty Raines is a thief and con artist whose life is always one wrong turn, one bad decision from implosion -- which is how she likes it. Fresh out of prison, she's attempting to stay afloat. But when she overhears a hit man being hired to kill a man's wife, she sets out to derail the job, sending her on a wild collision course with the charming killer and entangling them in dangerous, seductive relationship.
    







 







