ROHN Products, LLC - Self-Supporting Towers

















































Vertical Structures Built to Last.









 







+1 (309) 566-3000
+1 (800) 727-7646



























 





 







The World Leaders in Tower and Pole 
Design and Manufacturing









Self Supporting Towers 









Backed by one of the largest manufacturing facilities of communication towers in the world, ROHN self-supporting towers are produced with unmatched attention to detail. Our towers are hot-dip galvanized after fabrication to assure years of corrosion-free use.
In this process, ROHN tower manufacturing company immerses each section of the self-supporting tower in molten zinc, inside and out, until it's completely covered. Hot-dip galvanizing protects all points of welding and construction against rust and corrosion while providing an attractive finish.
ROHN manufacturers five self-supporting tower series including:
G- Series Self-Supporting Towers
RSL Self-Supporting Towers
SSV Self-Supporting Towers
SSMW Self-Supporting Towers
SSVSR Self-Supporting Towers
RS Self-Supporting Towers

























